00:38:04.970 --> 00:38:06.651
ALEX KOMOROSKE: One question.

00:38:06.651 --> 00:38:08.400
AUDIENCE: Are the
notification preferences

00:38:08.400 --> 00:38:11.754
synced across a user's
account or is it per device?

00:38:11.754 --> 00:38:13.170
ELISABETH MORANT:
It's per device.

00:38:13.170 --> 00:38:14.795
ALEX KOMOROSKE: And
the reason for that

00:38:14.795 --> 00:38:18.120
is the context that you opt
in is very device specific.

00:38:18.120 --> 00:38:20.520
So I might be interested
in seeing celebrity gossip

00:38:20.520 --> 00:38:22.610
on my personal-- because
I have a thing for that,

00:38:22.610 --> 00:38:25.380
apparently-- on my
personal machine,

00:38:25.380 --> 00:38:27.900
but I don't care
about it enough to be

00:38:27.900 --> 00:38:29.750
notified when I'm on the go.

00:38:29.750 --> 00:38:32.960
And so exactly where
the right user context

00:38:32.960 --> 00:38:35.380
depends on the device you're
in, and so it's not synced.

00:38:35.380 --> 00:38:37.213
AUDIENCE: And is the
notification preference

00:38:37.213 --> 00:38:40.819
per domain or per
specific website?

00:38:40.819 --> 00:38:42.610
ALEX KOMOROSKE: It's
per domain, basically.

00:38:42.610 --> 00:38:45.340
And so the idea is you want
to make sure as a site author

00:38:45.340 --> 00:38:48.122
that you use it
very respectfully.

00:38:48.122 --> 00:38:49.580
So one thing we
didn't show in this

00:38:49.580 --> 00:38:51.440
is the notifications
that show up

00:38:51.440 --> 00:38:53.750
have a very obvious
Site Settings button

00:38:53.750 --> 00:38:56.530
and if a user taps on that,
they're taken directly

00:38:56.530 --> 00:38:58.620
into Chrome Settings
for that domain, where

00:38:58.620 --> 00:39:01.910
it's a couple more taps
to revoke permissions

00:39:01.910 --> 00:39:02.800
for that domain.

00:39:02.800 --> 00:39:04.580
And so as a site
author, you want

00:39:04.580 --> 00:39:07.419
to make sure that you explain
to users what you're going to do

00:39:07.419 --> 00:39:09.460
and that you respect their
attention because it's

00:39:09.460 --> 00:39:11.260
very, very easy for
them-- of course,

00:39:11.260 --> 00:39:13.940
they're in control-- to
revoke permission very easily

00:39:13.940 --> 00:39:15.437
if you abuse it.

00:39:15.437 --> 00:39:16.270
AUDIENCE: Thank you.

